To build the entire GA toolkit package type,

	./gmake

in the top level directory.

Note:
----

Before building you must read the "HOW TO BUILD THE PACKAGE" 
section in the README file in the same directory and Chapter2
in GA user manual.
        http://www.emsl.pnl.gov/docs/global/user.html

Also, it is recommended to refer the file NOTES located in the 
same directory and also the GA support webpage:
        http://www.emsl.pnl.gov/docs/global/support.html

Help/Support:
------------
If you still have build problems contact the GA toolkit support.
email: hpctools@emsl.pnl.gov